HomeWiki:
Welcome!

This purpose of this project is to create a website/backend for storing and sharing gearing information, vehicle setups, and other misc radio control car information.

Users can store, share, and search gearing recommendations and setup information.

It will include services and APIs to allow others to build applications based on the database and logic that created here.

To view the current proposed feature list, go to Downloads then select "Planned" releases on the right-side.

Craig
